/* Table: "CON_DiscountTemplate" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "CON_DiscountTemplate"
(
"DisTemplateID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"RentTemplateID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"ZChargeCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"ZChargeName" NVARCHAR2(100) not null,
"TChargeCode2" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"TChargeName2" NVARCHAR2(100) not null,
"TermCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"TermName" NVARCHAR2(100) not null,
"DisShare" NUMBER(10,2) not null,
"TaxType" VARCHAR2(10) not null,
"TaxGroup" VARCHAR2(10) not null,
"FormulaCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"FormulaName" NVARCHAR2(100) not null,
"StartTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
"EndTime" TIMESTAMP not null,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
constraint PK_CON_DISCOUNTTEMPLATE primary key ("DisTemplateID")
);

comment on column "CON_DiscountTemplate"."Enable" is
'1:有效 0：无效';
